Title:
Happy new year!! ✨

Stoked for what’s ahead. 2023 was definitely a special year for us! Andami naming nasubukan at na experience na never sumagi sa isip naming mararanasan namin. 

We used to record all our songs ourselves - no fancy equipment and no producers at all. Pero thank God, we got to experience all of these last year! 🫶🏻 

Sobrang surreal to have the chance to work with our mastercakes producers, Choi Padilla, Nikhil Amarnani & Shadiel Chan. (hihi stay tuned sa upcoming song namin with sir shad) 🥹

Special thanks to Warner Music Philippines for making all of these happen! Special thanks din always to Sir Kelley, Sir Rem, and to everyone behind the team ✨

"Maria Clara" is a heartfelt track that beautifully captures the essence of appreciation for your special someone. With poetic lyrics, it elevates her to the standard of beauty, making every detail uniquely captivating. The melody becomes a serenade, weaving a musical escape where the presence of each other becomes a sanctuary, and a blissful refuge from the complexities of reality.

Performed by: Sugarcane, Cairo Peralta, Abner Badua, Jabez Lopez, Brad Coronel
Written by: Nijale Jizar T. Villa, Froilan Jerome DJ. Bautista, Cedric James A. Angeles
Produced by: Shadiel Chan
Mastered by: Jan Aries Agadier Fuertez
Art by: Felix Gasmen
Motion Graphics by: Rem Brofar
